<br>
<br>
I would suggest takeing manaburn as one of your latter AA's, as it is for the most part useless except in a group situation. In any case after you MB more than likely your going to be useing exodus to get your group out of a bad jam. There has been a very rare situation where in a raid MB would be useful. THO is one of those useful kills... but other than that, you can do well more damage with regular spellcasting.<br>
<br>
